        <h2>Where to book</h2>
        <p>For most family trips, one of these covers the flights, the room, or the whole package. Whole-home rentals (your own kitchen and bedrooms) are often the single best move for a dad traveling with kids — more space, fewer restaurant meals, and somewhere for them to crash early.</p>

